
This patch applies to "Speedball Cracktro" © 1988 Ackerlight

It requires WHDLoad 17+ and 512 KB ChipMem, QuitKey is F10.
Usual bugs removed (blitwait, aud.vol,...) and colors logo fixed on AGA.
It supports cracktro from different games, use CUSTOM1 option to select them.
Set CUSTOM1=1 for Atax & Growth
            2 for Captain Blood
            3 for Double Dragon
            4 for Espionage
            5 for Speedball
            6 for Video Generator Master

Cool intro for 1988! :)

Psygore in January 2013.
